Which of the following represents an accurate statement about stateless firewalls?
A)  Stateless firewalls have three zones: internal, external, and DMZ.
B)  Stateless firewalls are the only type available in Linux.
C)  Stateless firewalls examine packet headers to connect related packets.
D)  Stateless firewalls examine source and destination.
D
D. A stateless firewall examines only the source and destination and does not inspect ele-ments inside packets. Stateless firewalls are not typically associated with particular zonessuch as internal, external, or DMZ, thus making option A incorrect. Linux has firewallsthat can be configured as stateful, thus making option B incorrect.
